                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ar</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>divi Vespasian<del rend="erasure">i <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></del> <lb n="3"/><del rend="erasure">Domitianus</del> <lb n="4"/><del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan> Germanicus</del> <lb n="5"/>pontifex <expan><abbr>maxim</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure">XII</del> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure">XX</del>II co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure">XV</del>I <lb n="8"/>censor <expan><abbr>perp</abbr><ex>etuus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>faciend</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> curavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Lesung nach Alföldy. Z. 2 (Ende): NI in Ligatur; die beiden letzten Buchstaben wurden irrtümlich eradiert. Datierung: 14.9.92-13.9.93 n. Chr. (trib. pot. XII Domitians).</p>
